title: The Beatles Story (1973 BBC Radio Special)
description:
The Beatles Story

This is an unedited Radio Special that was produced in 1973 by the BBC in London. 
Hosted by Brian Matthew. The Beatles Story comes in 14 parts, approximately 45 
minutes each. Total time: 10 hours and 43 minutes. Bitrate: 128kbs.

Very Enjoyable. Some kinda 'Anthology' made in the 70's, 3 years after their 
split-up. Solid old style BBC radioprogram. A 20th century fairytale...
And, of course, with all music from vinyl.
